===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Hau (Masters)}}
Hau forms a [[sync pair]] with {{rf|Alolan}} {{p|Raichu}}, {{p|Tapu Koko}}, {{p|Crabominable}}, {{p|Incineroar}}, and {{p|Tauros}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Hau has been a playable sync pair since the game's release, with him joining the {{player}} after completing the eleventh chapter of the [[PML arc]].

Hau has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories: the PML arc, [[Legendary Adventures]], and the [[villain arc]].

